snippet.title: Umami Island - Trailer
snippet.description:
Available on https://sventomasek.itch.io/umami-island

Umami Island is an adventure farming game where you're stuck on an island with many secrets and are trying to find your way back home, but a giant sea monster is preventing you from leaving, until you fulfill the task it gave you.

/* Music used in the video */
Village Ambiance by Alexander Nakarada
